{"tid":1368683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［科學園開花］香港科技園公司員工 — 致特區領導層 - 勇於承擔 回應訴求","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:28:26.000Z","uid":8286,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1e84d3645d62449aa1011cd15459ec9000011b08","tid":1368683,"uid":8286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"作為推動本港科研及創業發展的主要公營機構，於過去多月來我們一眾團隊成員都緊守崗位，本著專業精神服務一眾創業家，ｓｔａｒｔｕｐ及科研人員。<br />\n<br />\n然而，特區領導層對人民及社會賢達訴求視而不見，以一己見孤行，致其他政府部門及公營機構手足於兩難，實非管治良策。又於過往週日發生元朗悲劇，人神共憤，加劇人民與政府之間亙不信任，做成更進一步人民鬥人民。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望特區領導層勇於站出來負起責任，解決困局，對香港人民負責，成立獨立調查委員會，完全撤回送中草案，負責任官員問責，好讓市民生活重回正軌，讓創業者及科研人員有一自由開放的安身立命之所。　<br />\n<br />\n香港科學園「園」工上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgC81DG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgC81DG.png&h=8d948251&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkndtiH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkndtiH.png&h=013f9d79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odqRZqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodqRZqo.png&h=e338edaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsefGDK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsefGDK.png&h=de829241&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7e9101d2b338d184cf1f5a12fd58e88687222d6","tid":1368683,"uid":8286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"個人名義: 至撚憎柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3551a2a094881ba1e57f2dd55cb78110445cc5ca","tid":1368683,"uid":35465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6418edc159ba3d5dbd3deccd6a7e7b9da937cb4","tid":1368683,"uid":60393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"科學園入面好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/fac